name: Cobra Tate Demolisher

Cobra Tate Demolisher

The Unofficial Game of Internet Sensation Andrew Tate.

The Unofficial Andrew Tate Game for Android and PC Bundled. Play as Cobra Tate fighting the Matrix. Rescue the Kids from the Matrix Cells and Earn An Andrew Tate Lesson after each level.   Old School 2D Arcade Shoot em up/Beat em up  Game 9 Levels   9 Bonus Levels    5 Boss Fights 11 Kick Ass Music Tracks   18 Tate Lessons    2 Game Versions - Android & PC Game in One Package
